				"number": "3",
				"title": "Differentialdiagnostik vid typisk astma och KOL",
				"text": "<table class=\"table table-bordered facts\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Astma</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>KOL</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Attacker, variabel obstruktivitet</td>\r\n<td>Successivt tilltagande och anstr&auml;ngningsutl&ouml;sta symtom</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Ofta debut i unga &aring;r</td>\r\n<td>Oftast debut efter 40 &aring;rs &aring;lder</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Eventuell allergi</td>\r\n<td>Tobaksexponering</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>K&auml;nslighet f&ouml;r irritanter</td>\r\n<td>Mer konstanta symtom</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Normalt status</td>\r\n<td>Tysta andningsljud, hypersonor perkussionston</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Normal eller helt reversibel spirometri</td>\r\n<td>Aldrig fullt reversibel spirometri</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Normal lungr&ouml;ntgen och DLCO</td>\r\n<td>Emfysembild samt l&aring;g DLCO</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>",
