				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Lindrig</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Måttlig</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Svår</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Livshotande</strong></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Symtom</span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Ansträngningsdyspné</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Samtalsdyspné</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Vilodyspné</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Uttalad dyspné<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">Fullständigt uttröttad </div><div class=\"tableLine\">eller konfusorisk</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Kan ligga ned</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Patienten vill sitta</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Sitter upprätt<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">Påverkat tal</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Svårt att tala</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Auxiliär andning</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Uttalad auxiliär andning</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Kliniska tecken</span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">PEF 75–85&#37;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">PEF 50–75&#37;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">PEF 30–50&#37;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">PEF &lt;&nbsp;30&#37;</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Puls 90–100 slag/minut</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Puls 100–120 slag/minut</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Puls &gt;&nbsp;120 slag/minut</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Bradykardi</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Ökad andningsfrekvens </div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">AF &gt;&nbsp;25 andetag/minut</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">AF &gt;&nbsp