			"content": "<h2 class=\"referenceHeader\" id=\"m1_137\">Referenser</h2>\n<ol class=\"references\"><li id=\"reference_1\">Dweik RA, Boggs PB, Erzurum SC, Irvin CG, Leigh MW, Lundberg JO, et al. An official ATS clinical practice guideline: interpretation of exhaled nitric oxide levels (FENO) for clinical applications. <a href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21885636\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"linkOut\">Am J Respir Crit Care Med. 2011;184:602&ndash;15.</a></li>\n<li id=\"reference_2\">Farmakologisk behandling vid astma. Information fr&aring;n L&auml;kemedelsverket. 2007:(18)Temanummer. <a href=\"http://www.lakemedelsverket.se/malgrupp/Halso---sjukvard/Behandlings--rekommendationer/Behandlingsrekommendation---listan/Astma/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"linkOut\">www.lakemedelsverket.se</a></li>\n<li id=\"reference_3\">Global strategy for asthma management and prevention, global initiative for asthma (GINA) 2012. <a href=\"http://www.ginasthma.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"linkOut\">www.ginasthma.org</a></li>\n<li id=\"reference_4\">Calverley PM, Anderson JA, Celli B, Ferguson GT, Jenkins C, Jones PW, et al. <a href=\"http://www.lakemedelsboken.se/atc/R03AC12\" data-atcid=\"R03AC12\" data-atctitles=\"Andningsorgan--Medel_vid_obstruktiva_luftv&#xE4;gssjukdomar--Adrenergika,_inhalationer--Selektiva_beta-2-stimulerande_medel--Salmeterol\" class=\"lb inlineGenerica text\">Salmeterol</a> and fluticasone propionate and survival in chronic obstructive pulmonary disease. <br><a href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17314337\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"linkOut\">N Engl J Med. 2007;356:775&ndash;89.</a></li>\n<li id=\"reference_5\">Tashkin DP, Celli B, Senn S, Burkhart D, Kesten S, Menjoge S, et al. A 4-year trial of tiotropium in chronic obstructive pulmonary disease. <br><a href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18836213\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"linkOut\">N Engl J Med. 2008;359:1543&ndash;54. </a></li>\n<li id=\"reference_6\">L&auml;kemedelsbehandling av kronisk obstruktiv lungsjukdom (KOL). Information fr&aring;n L&auml;kemedelsverket. 2009:(20)2. <br><a href=\"http://www.lakemedelsverket.se/malgrupp/Halso---sjukvard/Behandlings--rekommendationer/Behandlingsrekommendation---listan/KOL/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"linkOut\">www.lakemedelsverket.se</a></li>\n<li id=\"reference_7\">Rennard SI, Calverley PM, Goehring UM, Bredenbr&ouml;ker D, Martinez FJ. Reduction of exacerbations by the PDE4 inhibitor <a href=\"http://www.lakemedelsboken.se/atc/R03DX07\" data-atcid=\"R03DX07\" data-atctitles=\"Andningsorgan--Medel_vid_obstruktiva_luftv&#xE4;gssjukdomar--&#xD6;vriga_systemiska_medel_f&#xF6;r_obstruktiva_lungsjukdomar--&#xD6;vriga_systemiska_medel_f&#xF6;r_obstruktiva_lungsjukdomar--Roflumilast\" class=\"lb inlineGenerica text\">roflumilast</a> &ndash; the importance of defining different subsets of patients with COPD. <a href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21272339\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"linkOut\">Respir Res. 2011;12:18.</a></li>\n<li id=\"reference_8\">Decramer M, Rutten-van M&ouml;lken M, Dekhuijzen PN, Troosters T, van Herwaarden C, Pellegrino R, et al. Effects of N-<a href=\"http://www.lakemedelsboken.se/atc/R05CB01\" data-atcid=\"R05CB01\" data-atctitles=\"Andningsorgan--Medel_mot_hosta_och_f&#xF6;rkylning--Expektorantia,_exkl._kombinationer_med_hostd&#xE4;mpande_medel--Mukolytika--Acetylcystein\" class=\"lb inlineGenerica text\">acetylcystein</a>e on outcomes in chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (Bronchitis Randomized on NAC Cost-Utility Study, BRONCUS): a randomised placebo-controlled trial. <a href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15866309\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"linkOut\">Lancet. 2005;365:1552&ndash;60.</a></li>\n<li id=\"reference_9\">Anthonisen NR, Manfreda J, Warren CP, Hershfield ES, Harding GK, Nelson NA. Antibiotic therapy in exacerbations of chronic obstructive pulmonary disease. <br><a href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=anthonisen%20nr%20and%20antibiotic%20and%201987\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"linkOut\">Ann Intern Med. 1987;106:196&ndash;204.</a></li>\n<li id=\"reference_10\">Chauhan BF, Chartrand C, Ducharme FM. Intermittent versus daily inhaled corticosteroids for persistent asthma in children and adults.<br> <a href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23450606\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"linkOut\">Coch rane Database Syst Rev. 2013;2:CD009611.</a></li>\n</ol>",
